      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently has a noticeable knock and struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission exhibits slipping during gear changes. Externally, the body shows signs of rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively on the hood and roof. The interior has heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project car for a mechanic or a source for parts, but it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
