    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride, perfect for someone looking for a solid vehicle at a great price! It's in fair condition and has been a reliable companion, showing some expected signs of wear and tear both inside and out. It's a functional, honest car that's ready to get you where you need to go with plenty of life left in it!",
